response.original_title: Bail Up! The Bushranger on Australia's Silent Screen (1906-1928)
response.overview: A collection of early Australian films about bushrangers, compiled by Australia's National Film and Sound Archive.  Films are: [unknown] (1906), The Story of the Kelly Gang (1906), The Story of the Kelly Gang (1910), Thunderbolt (1910), Trooper Campbell (1914), The Kelly Gang (1920), Robbery Under Arms (1920),  When The Kellys Were Out (1923), and Trooper O'Brien (1928).

production_companies.name: National Film and Sound Archive of Australia (NFSA)
